# The MetaGPT repo root .gitignore excludes *.png, but the bundled maze +
# character assets ARE part of this standalone project and must be tracked.
# (This negation is scoped to backend/assets so stray *.png elsewhere stay
# ignored.)
!backend/assets/**/*.png

